cs.HCI, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.CE 

The paper focuses on improving the quality of results on microtask crowdsourcing platforms, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction (cs.HCI). The paper also discusses the role of requesters in low-quality work, which is related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper proposes a new crowdsourcing strategy, which involves iterative task design, which is related to computational linguistics (cs.CL) and computer engineering (cs.CE).
